In this repo, we use docker engine api within a container (named docker-engine-api-example) to create and start a new nginx container on the docker host.

Usage:

## 1. Build docker image

```
./build.sh
```

## 2. Execution
```
docker-compose up
or
docker run -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock bennylu/docker-engine-api-example
```

## 3. See if a new nginx container is started

```
docker ps
```